author: Climate Town
description: Not much shocks people these days, but hearing about how much perfectly good food America sends to the dump will usually do the trick. And double bonus, that decomposing food is one of the biggest sources of landfill methane. Emissions from your food waste is one of the few things you can actually make a dent in, so eat all the food you buy and visit our friends & the sponsor of this video @mill over at www.mill.com
title: We Waste SOOO Much Food
